{"tid":1782850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"皇仁書院舊生會召周年大會250人出席　消息︰83%同意廢何君堯會籍","createTime":"2019-12-14T10:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T20:39:22.000Z","uid":28114,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"40acd1cfe8efe50ae668c7be45cc3158f17f8131","tid":1782850,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3704091/org/86a0ec802d24efcae59f891a2d1d441e.jpg/WomnoZbLQX3ObdfQYsB9Btq3tduQkiJD1W_X0dVv19E?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3704091%2Forg%2F86a0ec802d24efcae59f891a2d1d441e.jpg%2FWomnoZbLQX3ObdfQYsB9Btq3tduQkiJD1W_X0dVv19E%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=f4c3d764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息指，立法會議員何君堯的母校皇仁書院，舊生會下午召開周年會員大會，近250人出席，期間有約10名會員先後發言，大部份贊同終止何君堯的會籍。據了解，會長易永源在會上表示，早前的諮詢有約780人回覆問卷，當中超過83%贊同終止其會籍，今日選出的新任執委會會繼續跟進。<br />\n<br />\n7月21日晚元朗區有白衣人無差別襲擊西鐵元朗站市民，同一夜立法會議員何君堯被拍攝到向疑似施襲者鼓掌豎拇指，盛讚其為「英雄」，他其後解釋當晚是在襲擊前行經該處。何君堯的母校皇仁書院，有大批舊生及學生在報章刊登聯署，強烈譴責何君堯。<br />\n<br />\n皇仁舊生會並於8月29日向所有會員發電郵，指超過2,500名學生及舊生透過簽名活動及各渠道所表達的意見清晰而明確；對於會否廢除何君堯會籍，舊生會表示要透過問卷諮詢會員。<br />\n<br />\n3/4執委通過可終止會籍<br />\n<br />\n根據《皇仁舊生會會憲》第8(1)(b)條，會員若行為不當或其操守可能損害皇仁舊生會的聲譽或利益，而經出席執委會會議的執委四分之三多數通過，其會籍即告終止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/410019/皇仁書院舊生會召周年大會250人出席-消息-83-同意廢何君堯會籍?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F410019%2F%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2%E8%88%8A%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%AC%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83250%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-83-%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E5%BB%A2%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E6%9C%83%E7%B1%8D%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dnews&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=4f95bf71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/410019/皇仁書院舊生會召周年大會250人出席-消息-83-同意廢何君堯會籍?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news</a>"},{"pid":"0725a40e7be46317c9aa9c47088f2dc50b40b061","tid":1782850,"uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"又QD，狂賀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcc720b35b0f946f19123c4275b7963cbb56acf","tid":1782850,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e629bb034cb2dc21c76057db9bba8fd0e02ee393","tid":1782850,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4dff50bd2304579b9b40872a79b039ad355427f3","tid":1782850,"uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恥與為伍</span>"},{"pid":"a70414507d808228ae661adfe01fa70bbce2cd8b","tid":1782850,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f0effdd893aa5b14d7b1f6c76a9e0e9addd92c","tid":1782850,"uid":2654,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"俾個社會清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr